Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:01.50,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,=========OP==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.66,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}当我闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:40.11,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}一切都是那么令我感到惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:44.51,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}他们的身影又再度清楚浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:49.31,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}活生生出现在我的银幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:54.12,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我爱人的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:58.78,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我战斗时的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:08.11,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}全部都在我的脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:13.29,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我们一天的时间 让我们找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:17.57,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}引领到你世界的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.51,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我一个晚上 让你能再看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:26.01,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我就会相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:30.04,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:36.03,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,2000)}{\be1}回忆啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:01.50,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,=========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:23.03,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}没有地图 也没有罗盘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:28.07,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我们 扬帆出航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:37.61,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}并非去寻找既有的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:48.12,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}而是创造全新世界之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:58.30,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}过去的旅途仍记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:04.37,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}不论是哪一段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:11.71,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}都是一段很热闹的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.99,0:24:33.96,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回头望去 旅程激起的波浪浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.00,0:24:40.17,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}以温和的口吻 称读我的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.24,0:24:47.88,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}这么对我说着 发出灿烂光芒
